SQL_STMT_U.val:
select distinct Artikel, LagerNr,matchcode, matchcodez, Techniker, isnull(Bestand,0) as Bestand,isnull(mindest_Bestand,0) as MinBestand,isnull(maximaler_Bestand,0) as MaxBestand from (select ':11' as Artikel, nl.LagerNr, kd.Matchcode, kz.Matchcode as MatchcodeZ, isnull(mi.Techniker,0) as Techniker, nl.Bestand, nl.mindest_Bestand, nl.maximaler_Bestand from nebenlager nl WITH(NOLOCK) inner join ebene4 e WITH(NOLOCK) on (e.Ebene1=nl.Ebene1 and e.Ebene2=nl.Ebene2 and e.Ebene3=nl.Ebene3 and e.Ebene4=nl.Ebene4) left join kunden kd WITH(NOLOCK) on (kd.Ebene1=nl.Ebene1 and kd.Ebene2=nl.Ebene2 and kd.Ebene3=nl.Ebene3 and kd.Ebene4=nl.Ebene4 and kd.KDNR= case when nl.LagerNr=0 then 1 else nl.LagerNr end) left join kunden kz WITH(NOLOCK) on (kz.Ebene1=e.ZentralEbene1 and kz.Ebene2=e.ZentralEbene2 and kz.Ebene3=e.ZentralEbene3 and kz.Ebene4=e.ZentralEbene4 and kz.KDNR= case when nl.LagerNr=0 then 1 else nl.LagerNr end) left join mitarbeiter mi WITH(NOLOCK) on (mi.Ebene1=e.ZentralEbene1 and mi.Ebene2=e.ZentralEbene2 and mi.Ebene3=e.ZentralEbene3 and mi.Ebene4=e.ZentralEbene4 and mi.Nebenlager_Nr>0 and mi.Nebenlager_Nr=nl.LagerNr) :5 left outer join GESCHAEFTSF_GESP_LG ls WITH(NOLOCK) on (ls.Ebene1=e.ZentralEbene1 and ls.Ebene2=e.ZentralEbene2 and ls.Ebene3=e.ZentralEbene3 and ls.Ebene4=e.ZentralEbene4 and ls.gesperrtesLager=nl.LagerNr and ls.Geschaeftsfall=':8') where nl.Ebene1=:1 and nl.Ebene2=:2 and nl.Ebene3=:3 and nl.Ebene4=:4 and nl.ArtikelNr=':11' :6 :7
union
select ':11' as Artikel, case when nl.Lager_Nr=1 then 0 else nl.Lager_Nr end as LagerNr, kd.Matchcode, kz.Matchcode as MatchcodeZ, isnull(mi.Techniker,0) as Techniker,isnull(lb.Bestand,0) as Bestand,isnull(lb.mindest_Bestand,0) as MinBestand,isnull(lb.maximaler_Bestand,0) as MaxBestand from LAGERBESCHREIBUNG nl WITH(NOLOCK) inner join ebene4 e WITH(NOLOCK) on (e.Ebene1=nl.Ebene1 and e.Ebene2=nl.Ebene2 and e.Ebene3=nl.Ebene3 and e.Ebene4=nl.Ebene4) left join kunden kd WITH(NOLOCK) on (kd.Ebene1=nl.Ebene1 and kd.Ebene2=nl.Ebene2 and kd.Ebene3=nl.Ebene3 and kd.Ebene4=nl.Ebene4 and kd.KDNR= case when nl.Lager_Nr=0 then 1 else nl.Lager_Nr end) left join kunden kz WITH(NOLOCK) on (kz.Ebene1=e.ZentralEbene1 and kz.Ebene2=e.ZentralEbene2 and kz.Ebene3=e.ZentralEbene3 and kz.Ebene4=e.ZentralEbene4 and kz.KDNR= case when nl.Lager_Nr=0 then 1 else nl.Lager_Nr end) left join mitarbeiter mi WITH(NOLOCK) on (mi.Ebene1=e.ZentralEbene1 and mi.Ebene2=e.ZentralEbene2 and mi.Ebene3=e.ZentralEbene3 and mi.Ebene4=e.ZentralEbene4 and mi.Nebenlager_Nr>0 and mi.Nebenlager_Nr=nl.Lager_Nr) :9 left outer join GESCHAEFTSF_GESP_LG ls WITH(NOLOCK) on (ls.Ebene1=e.ZentralEbene1 and ls.Ebene2=e.ZentralEbene2 and ls.Ebene3=e.ZentralEbene3 and ls.Ebene4=e.ZentralEbene4 and ls.gesperrtesLager=nl.Lager_Nr and ls.Geschaeftsfall=':8') left outer join NEBENLAGER lb WITH(NOLOCK) on (lb.Ebene1=nl.Ebene1 and lb.Ebene2=nl.Ebene2 and lb.Ebene3=nl.Ebene3 and lb.Ebene4=nl.Ebene4 and lb.LagerNr=case when nl.Lager_Nr=1 then 0 else nl.Lager_Nr end and lb.ArtikelNr=':11') where nl.Ebene1=:1 and nl.Ebene2=:2 and nl.Ebene3=:3 and nl.Ebene4=:4 :10 ) a order by Bestand desc,LagerNr
